data.message: Top design resource ecosystem: Study materials (ui.glass, bentogrids.com, Material Design 3, Figma Resource Library), Tools (Coolors, CSS Gradient, Mesher, shadcn/ui, Lucide), Design Systems to reference (Material Design 3, Apple HIG, Carbon, Fluent). Hype4 Academy's Michal Malewicz coined "glassmorphism".
